article.headline: Tennessee State 83, Morehead State 75
article.story: MOREHEAD, Ky. (AP) -- Kareem Grant scored 24 points to lead Tennessee State to an 83-75 win over Morehead State on Thursday night. Tennessee State (12-14, 10-9 Ohio Valley Conference) led by as much as 19 points in the second half before Morehead State (4-22, 3-16) pulled to within six late in the game. But the Eagles could get no closer. There were six ties and eight lead changes in the first half before Tennessee State pulled away to a 38-32 halftime lead. Wayne Arnold finished with 17 points for Tennessee State, and Clarence Matthews had 13 points and 10 rebounds. Tyke Cockerham led Morehead State with 20 points. Shaun Williams scored 19 and Stan Januska 13.
